Package: kgFRA
Title: Financial Risk Analysis Package - analyze your stocks!
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Kamil", "Golis", , "kamil.d.golis@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package is intended to enable user to analyze stocks in terms of financial risk. It contains functions to plot prices and daily returns, calculate summary statistics, Risk-Adjusted Performance Measures, Value at Risk and Expected Shortfall. The stocks are accessed via quantmod package.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports: quantmod, stats, PerformanceAnalytics
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
